<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="Template_Navbox_translation" title="Template:Navbox translation"><span title="View this template" style="">v</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-talk"><a href="../../w/index-title=Template_talk_Navbox_translation&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="Template talk:Navbox translation (page does not exist)"><span title="Discuss this template" style="">t</span></a></li>
